sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant K8sAuth as K8s API Server<br/>(SAR Check)
    participant Fastify as Fastify BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModReg as model-registry-ui<br/>8043/TCP HTTPS
    participant GenAI as gen-ai-ui<br/>8143/TCP HTTPS
    participant Perses as data-science-perses<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Thanos as Thanos Querier<br/>9092/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 1: User Accessing Dashboard UI

    Browser->>Gateway: GET / (HTTPS/443)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>Forwarded user token
    KRBP->>K8sAuth: SubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/443, SA token<br/>Can user list projects?
    K8sAuth-->>KRBP: Allowed
    KRBP->>Fastify: HTTP/8080 (localhost)<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups
    Fastify-->>KRBP: React SPA + static assets
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS response

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 2: Kubernetes API Passthrough

    Browser->>Gateway: POST /api/k8s/apis/kubeflow.org/v1/notebooks<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token: user-token
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Authorization: Bearer user-token
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: JSON Response
    Fastify-->>KRBP: HTTP Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: HTTPS Response
    Gateway-->>Browser: HTTPS Response

    Note over Browser,ModReg: Flow 3: Module Federation (Model Registry UI)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /model-registry/api/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: HTTP/8080<br/>x-forwarded-access-token
    Fastify->>ModReg: HTTPS/8043<br/>TLS (service-ca)<br/>x-forwarded-access-token header
    ModReg->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443<br/>Bearer user-token
    K8sAPI-->>ModReg: Response
    ModReg-->>Fastify: Response
    Fastify-->>Browser: Response (via KRBP + Gateway)

    Note over Browser,K8sAPI: Flow 4: WebSocket Watch

    Browser->>Gateway: Upgrade /wss/k8s/...<br/>WSS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: WSS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: WS/8080<br/>Token via subprotocol
    Fastify->>K8sAPI: WSS/443<br/>Bearer token via subprotocol
    K8sAPI-->>Fastify: Watch events (streaming)
    Fastify-->>Browser: Watch events (streaming)

    Note over Browser,Perses: Flow 5: Observability Proxy (Perses)

    Browser->>Gateway: GET /perses/api/...<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>KRBP: HTTPS/8443
    KRBP->>Fastify: HTTP/8080
    Fastify->>Perses: HTTP/8080<br/>No encryption<br/>User token passthrough
    Perses-->>Fastify: Dashboard data
    Fastify-->>Browser: Response (via KRBP + Gateway)

    Note over Fastify,Thanos: Background: Metrics Queries

    Fastify->>Thanos: HTTPS/9092<br/>TLS<br/>ServiceAccount token
    Thanos-->>Fastify: Prometheus metrics
